feat: Enhance FileSystemAgent and agent interaction framework

- Implemented a new dynamic command handling mechanism to support enhanced user interactions and requests.
- Integrated additional error handling for improved robustness during file interactions.
- Updated vectorization methods in FileSystemAgent for better intent recognition and command processing.
- Refined the structure of prompt data to dynamically include the user's current working context and directory.
- Enhanced suggest_function to generate initial responses for proposed new functionalities, increasing user engagement.
- Improved system messaging in response management with better prompts and feedback alignment.

This commit aims to streamline various functionalities within the FileSystemAgent and make the chatbot's interactions more user-friendly and context-aware, enhancing the overall experience.